# Memory layer audit

## Caps

- Any CLAUDE.md: 200 lines (adherence drops past this)
- MEMORY.md: 200 lines OR 25 KB (past that is invisible at session start)

## Discipline

- One-line entries in MEMORY.md; detail in linked topic files
- Skill descriptions answer WHEN, not WHAT
- Resolve sync-conflict files manually
- Periodic audit (~monthly)
